item.description:
@supra_s wrote:

emote tabs -> if you press on the emote tab something happens or a number appears in your run.bat

IF SOMETHING HAPPENS SEARCH THAT UP IN YOUR CLIENT (srry for caps pressd on xD)

if you get a numbers search in client.java for “case” then add one of your self start end end with ->

  • start:
    Case ####:

  • add here what you want

  • end:
    Break;
